# PEAR2\Math\TrigOp
 
This packages includes:

- A class with static methods that implement supplementary trigonometric,
  inverse trigonometric, hyperbolic, and inverse hyperbolic functions.
- An exception class used by the static methods

**It does not have, yet, a unit test fixture **


The package http://pear.php.net/package/Math_TrigOp and has been migrated
from http://svn.php.net/repository/pear/packages/Math_TrigOp

Please report all new issues via the PEAR bug tracker.

To test, run either
$ phpunit tests/
  or
$ pear run-tests -r

To build, simply
$ pear package

To install from scratch
$ pear install package.xml

To upgrade
$ pear upgrade -f package.xml
